{"tid":1979063,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"【迷思】有痠痛才有練到嗎？","createTime":"2020-04-19T07:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T06:41:03.000Z","uid":37397,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"22a9651bf5f0df2f8e4682e76bdce666422e2aa1","tid":1979063,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:11:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://one-minutefitness.blogspot.com/2014/07/blog-post_13.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fone-minutefitness.blogspot.com%2F2014%2F07%2Fblog-post_13.html&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=51e53014\" target=\"_blank\">http://one-minutefitness.blogspot.com/2014/07/blog-post_13.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【迷思】有痠痛才有練到嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">肌肉酸痛與運動成效</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">儘管上面兩張圖告訴我們「痠痛組」真的吃了比較多苦，但是最後的成績<br />\n<br />\n兩組的力量進步幅度相近<br />\n兩組的肌肉體積增加幅度相近<br />\n<br />\n如果酸痛不會讓您更強壯，也不會讓肌肉長得更大塊，何必要讓自己吃那麼多苦呢？No pain 可不一定 No gain！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">酸痛時可不可以運動？</span>"},{"pid":"cce6c54f8b31c776ddc29bb130dfb179f51c4083","tid":1979063,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"c13f56a1c294b913df2314319e964d4f38b284a2","tid":1979063,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T15:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ibw.bwnet.com.tw/image/pool/2015/12/930335686ea380b6524ba0acc83281a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fibw.bwnet.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fpool%2F2015%2F12%2F930335686ea380b6524ba0acc83281a1.jpg&h=bb46be2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ibw.bwnet.com.tw/image/pool/2015/12/aa5910bbbb4180dcf66a5771ca26f58c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fibw.bwnet.com.tw%2Fimage%2Fpool%2F2015%2F12%2Faa5910bbbb4180dcf66a5771ca26f58c.jpg&h=32b82d4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e9682c494cca2cbd8565b4a7ca69ceb